Functions:
A specific set of instructions to perform a well defined tasks.

◻ Declaration
  ▫ Return Type (int ,float,char..)
  ▫ Name of the function
  ▫ Set of Parameters

Ex - Declare a method that adds two integrs to it. 
      int add(int a,int b);

Method definition:
  actual logic / functionality of the function / method

  int add(int a,int b)
  {
      int c = a + b;
      return c;
  }

  ** Keyword  RETURN to return the value of the function


       
        
        
         


